Compile a Program

Source: R/client.R
pjrt_compile.Rd

Compile a PJRTProgram program into a PJRTExecutable.

Usage

pjrt_compile(
  program,
  compile_options = new_compile_options(),
  client = pjrt_client()
)

Arguments

program

(character(1))
A program to compile.

compile_options

(PJRTCompileOptions)
Compile options.

client

(PJRTClient | character(1))
A PJRT client object or the name of the platform to use ("cpu", "cuda", ...), from which the client will be created.

Value

PJRTExecutable
